# Ignore all timestamped directories/files in any output folder
**/output/**/*_*-*-*

# More specifically, catch all common timestamp patterns:
**/output/**/*[0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9]-[0-9][0-9]-[0-9][0-9]*
**/output/**/*[0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9]_[0-9][0-9]_[0-9][0-9]*


